<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ProDhee</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%@ include file="header.jsp" %>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect information you provide directly such as name, email, phone number, and payment information when you create an account or enroll in courses.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use the information to provide services, process transactions, send updates, and comply with legal obligations.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">3. Information Sharing</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We only share with service providers who assist us in operating the platform.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We implement security measures to protect your information against unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information by logging into your account.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%@ include file="footer.jsp" %>
